item.title: Women in STEM
item.description: I have always loved Cindi Lauper’s style and her iconic song, ‘Girls just want to have fun’, and when I saw this photo (see above) from the Women’s March, I knew I needed to make my own rendition of the song. I hope you enjoy! I originally learned how to play the song on the ukulele following this tutorial. The lyrics and tabs below: __ Women in STEM
